\contentsline {paragraph}{1. Wrong UI code does not compile.}{7}{section.1.7}%
\contentsline {paragraph}{2. Re-drawing is wired to be fast.}{8}{lstnumber.-1.1}%
\contentsline {paragraph}{3. The runtime is borrowed from a language called Elm.}{8}{lstnumber.-1.1}%
